Compilation flags for xkaapi :

release mode :

./configure --enable-mode=release
            --enable-target=mt
            --with-steal=cas
            --disable-network
            --enable-api-kaapixx=no
            --enable-api-kastl=no
            --enable-api-atha=no
            --prefix=/home/claferri/opt/release/
debug mode :

./configure --enable-mode=debug
            --enable-target=mt
            --with-steal=cas
            --disable-network
            --with-perfcounter
            --enable-api-kaapixx=no
            --enable-api-kastl=no
            --enable-api-atha=no
            --prefix=/home/claferri/opt/debug/

***********************************************************

Compilation flags for C2X :

- C2X_USES_TIMING
- C2X_USES_GTG

Compilation flags for MJPEG :

- _USE_TRACE (get the first trace format that has to be converted with
  convert.py from Lucas).
- MJPEG_USES_TIMING
- MJPEG_USES_GTG

